            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once evaporated, add the <strong>miso stock </strong>to the pan a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for 25-30 min or until all of the stock is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Meanwhile, drain your<strong> king prawns</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1687782649247-x200.jpg",
