          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1687782652574-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1687782652574-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Japanese-style king prawn & miso risotto</strong> in a bowl, discard the lime leaf[ves]</p><p>Drizzle over your <strong>soy</strong> <strong>sauce</strong> and garnish with your <strong>shichimi togarashi </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
